{"tid":1709986,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【黃/藍經濟】50+Ben Sir自爆未跟美心割席 純粹貪方便","createTime":"2019-11-12T04:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T06:23:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ed51870f1d91d72e51d276bbc44fd509b364844a","tid":1709986,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"曾任中大中文系高級講師的「Ben Sir」歐陽偉豪，他不時在社交網分享對社會運動的個人意見，對於網民不時發起撐黃店，Ben Sir昨晚都在facebook講起「黃色經濟」，他竟自爆未跟美心割席。Ben Sir留言：「上個禮拜我哋啲中同行山，講開黃色經濟。我哋呢代（50+），縱使政治上係黃，但經濟未去到分顏色，嗰日朝我都係去美心買蛋糕，因為地鐵裏面實在方便。我知道唔完美，可接受，有改善空間，唔好同我割！」<br />\n<br />\nBen Sir再仔細分析：<br />\n50歲+：黃政治，黃/藍經濟<br />\n40-50歲：黃政治，黃經濟<br />\n30-40歲：黃政治，黃經濟，黃/藍文化<br />\n20-30歲：黃政治，黃經濟，黃娛樂文化，黃交通，黃大學...<br />\n<br />\nBen Sir：「再說用顏色主導政經民生，冇話好唔好，但亦唔需要排斥。最緊要都係：唔理黃藍，廣東話一定要攬。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191112/large/1573531224_312d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191112%2Flarge%2F1573531224_312d.jpg&h=aa4f63ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191112/60257370\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191112%2F60257370&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYiDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=143cf1e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191112%2F60257370&h=744a0945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191112/60257370</a>"},{"pid":"16b2ab670ade87ba2fae6fbd4f1cbf2205927758","tid":1709986,"uid":42848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:59:24.000Z","msg":"知道可改善就唔好搵籍口幫自己兜啦"},{"pid":"74a6603a487d3edd63ac7566c3b640f2924ae01e","tid":1709986,"uid":135041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:01:51.000Z","msg":"美心蛋糕好難